<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 12:27:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管需求疲软，电动汽车公司 Polestar 仍预计第四季度毛利率将为正</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-firm-polestar-expects-positive-fourth-quarter-gross-margin-despite-slow-2024-10-11/</link><description>Polestar周五表示，尽管第三季度电动汽车交付量下降14%，但预计第四季度将实现正毛利率。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-firm-polestar-expects-positive-fourth-quarter-gross-margin-despite-slow-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>在紧张的美国大选中什么对世界市场最重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-matters-most-world-markets-tight-us-election-race-2024-10-11/</link><description>美国总统大选是选举密集的一年中对金融市场最重要的投票，距离大选还有几周的时间。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:31:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-matters-most-world-markets-tight-us-election-race-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>印尼要求苹果、谷歌屏蔽中国Temu以保护小商户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/indonesia-asks-apple-google-block-chinas-temu-protect-small-merchants-2024-10-11/</link><description>一位部长周五表示，印度尼西亚已要求 Alphabet 旗下的谷歌和苹果在该国的应用程序商店中屏蔽中国快时尚电子商务公司 Temu，使其无法下载。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/indonesia-asks-apple-google-block-chinas-temu-protect-small-merchants-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>TomTom首席执行官表示，中国贸易紧张局势给汽车制造商的投资计划蒙上了阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-trade-tensions-cast-shadow-automakers-investment-plans-tomtom-ceo-says-2024-10-11/</link><description>数字地图专家 TomTom 的首席执行官周五表示，中国和西方之间的贸易紧张局势抑制了汽车制造商的投资决策和长期前景，给该行业带来了一定程度的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-trade-tensions-cast-shadow-automakers-investment-plans-tomtom-ceo-says-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 Temu 提供有关打击非法产品销售所采取措施的信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-told-by-eu-give-info-steps-it-is-taking-against-illegal-product-sales-2024-10-11/</link><description>欧盟委员会表示，已根据《数字服务法》(DSA) 向购物网站 Temu 发出信息请求，要求 Temu 提供其为阻止在其平台上销售非法产品而采取的措施的信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-told-by-eu-give-info-steps-it-is-taking-against-illegal-product-sales-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着大银行报告，美联储“跳过”进入竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-11/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国和越南将签署铁路、农业协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnam-set-sign-deals-railway-links-agriculture-sources-say-2024-10-11/</link><description>两位了解相关计划的人士称，中国总理李强本周末访问河内期间，中国和越南预计将签署新协议，包括促进铁路连接和农产品贸易的协议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:45:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnam-set-sign-deals-railway-links-agriculture-sources-say-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>法国白兰地生产商准备应对中欧贸易争端的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/frances-cognac-beijing-brussels-ev-spat-spells-disaster-2024-10-11/</link><description>在法国西部的这个葡萄种植区，白兰地生产商正为欧盟与中国之间的贸易争端的影响而苦恼，而科涅克白兰地这个小镇也笼罩着阴郁的气氛，法国最著名的白兰地就以这个小镇的名字命名。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/frances-cognac-beijing-brussels-ev-spat-spells-disaster-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车交付量下降凸显欧洲汽车业面临的挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-q3-deliveries-down-confirming-challenges-european-auto-sector-2024-10-11/</link><description>大众汽车集团周五报告称，第三季度全球交付量下降7%，显示欧洲汽车行业正面临严峻挑战，包括中国需求疲软和国内生产成本高企。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-q3-deliveries-down-confirming-challenges-european-auto-sector-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>央行机构呼吁更详细地监控银行流动性风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/central-bank-body-calls-more-detailed-monitoring-bank-liquidity-risks-2024-10-11/</link><description>国际清算银行周五在对去年银行业动荡的研究中表示，银行监管机构应确保全球银行的各个实体拥有充足的流动性，而不仅仅是监控集团层面的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 08:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/central-bank-body-calls-more-detailed-monitoring-bank-liquidity-risks-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>两名涉嫌策划 2021 年袭击中国人的巴基斯坦武装分子在枪战中丧生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-suspected-pakistani-militants-behind-2021-attack-chinese-killed-shootout-2024-10-11/</link><description>反恐官员称，两名参与 2021 年袭击、造成 9 名中国工程师死亡的武装分子周五在巴基斯坦中部地区的一次枪战中被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-suspected-pakistani-militants-behind-2021-attack-chinese-killed-shootout-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国刺激计划的不确定性影响欧洲股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-stocks-dip-china-caution-sets-french-markets-lag-2024-10-11/</link><description>由于紧张的投资者等待中国刺激计划的最新消息，欧洲股市周五下跌，而法国股市在政府公布旨在解决不断上升的财政赤字的 2025 年预算后小幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:24:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-stocks-dip-china-caution-sets-french-markets-lag-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷9个月中国销量下滑三分之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-nine-month-china-sales-plunge-by-third-2024-10-11/</link><description>德国跑车制造商保时捷 (Porsche) 周五公布，其在华销量连续 9 个月下降 29%，与宝马和梅赛德斯 (Mercedes) 等同行一样，其在华销量也表现疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-nine-month-china-sales-plunge-by-third-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于节日吸引买家，亚洲黄金印度价格在两个月后出现溢价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-prices-premium-after-two-months-festive-season-draws-buyers-2024-10-11/</link><description>由于即将到来的节日季吸引了一些金饰购买，而疲软的消费者信心抑制了中国节后的需求，印度实物黄金交易商本周两个月来首次收取溢价。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:46:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-prices-premium-after-two-months-festive-season-draws-buyers-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>巴克莱银行：中国股市每周资金流入创历史新高，日本股市出现20年来最大流出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-equities-see-record-weekly-inflows-japan-has-biggest-outflow-20-years-2024-10-11/</link><description>巴克莱援引 EPFR 的数据表示，截至周三的一周，新兴市场股票的资金流入创历史新高，其中中国股市的资金流入创纪录。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-equities-see-record-weekly-inflows-japan-has-biggest-outflow-20-years-2024-10-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>